---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="HeartStrings App - Digital Companion to HeartStrings Play"
  description="HeartStrings App is the digital companion to HeartStrings Play. Profiles, guided matching, and compatibility rationale powered by AIya and AIon. In development by ByteLite LLC."
  keywords={["HeartStrings App", "HeartStrings companion", "AIya", "AIon", "matching app", "compatibility", "ByteLite LLC", "HeartStrings Play"]}
  schemaType="SoftwareApplication"
>

  <!-- App Hero -->
  <section class="app-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <div class="hero-gradient"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <span class="dev-pill">In Development</span>
          <h1>HeartStrings App</h1>
          <p class="hero-tagline">HeartStrings is the original product. HeartStrings Play is the launch-first consumer front door. The app is the full compatibility and consent system.</p>
          <p class="hero-sub">80-question personality assessment. 6-bit binary vector privacy-preserving matching. Powered by ByteLite infrastructure and Deep Kore intelligence.</p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-rose">Express Interest</a>
            <a href="/heartstrings" class="btn btn-pink-outline">See HeartStrings Play</a>
            <a href="/status" class="btn btn-outline">Current Status</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-preview">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-app-signup.png"
            alt="HeartStrings App login screen"
            width="300"
            height="500"
            decoding="async"
            class="app-screen-img"
          />
          <div class="screen-badge">UI Design -- Prototype</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What the App Does -->
  <section class="app-what">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="app-logo-row">
        <img
          src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-app-logo.png"
          alt="HeartStrings App"
          width="80"
          height="80"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="app-logo-img"
        />
        <h2>What the App Does</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-lead">HeartStrings App is the digital layer that extends what you start in HeartStrings Play. It is a companion, not a replacement.</p>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon pink">profile</div>
          <h3>Profiles and Preferences</h3>
          <p>Build a structured profile that captures what you actually value -- not interests lists, but real dimensions that drive compatibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon rose">match</div>
          <h3>Guided Matching</h3>
          <p>AIya and AIon guide the match process. Compatibility rationale is explicit -- you see exactly why a match scores where it does.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon purple">connect</div>
          <h3>Play Continuity</h3>
          <p>Sessions from HeartStrings Play can extend into the app. What you discovered in person becomes context for your digital interaction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon cyan">layers</div>
          <h3>ByteLite Infrastructure</h3>
          <p>The app runs on ByteLite compression infrastructure, enabling efficient AI model deployment even for smaller development teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bridge from Play -->
  <section class="play-bridge">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bridge-inner">
        <div class="bridge-flow">
          <div class="flow-step step-play">
            <div class="flow-icon">01</div>
            <div class="flow-label">HeartStrings Play</div>
            <p>Physical board game session. Navigate the heart-shaped board, draw card tiers, build real chemistry. AIya and AIon host.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">-&gt;</div>
          <div class="flow-step step-app">
            <div class="flow-icon">02</div>
            <div class="flow-label">HeartStrings App</div>
            <p>Digital companion. Profiles, match rationale, and guided interaction powered by the same AIya and AIon guides.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">-&gt;</div>
          <div class="flow-step step-infra">
            <div class="flow-icon">03</div>
            <div class="flow-label">ByteLite + Deep Kore</div>
            <p>Infrastructure and intelligence layer underneath. Compression enables efficient deployment. Deep Kore powers future AI depth.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="bridge-caption">Play is the first chapter. The app is what comes next.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AIya + AIon in the App -->
  <section class="app-guides">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guides-inner">
        <div class="guides-visual">
          <div class="guide-pair">
            <div class="guide-profile">
              <img
                src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-aiya-icon.png"
                alt="AIya"
                width="100"
                height="100"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                class="guide-icon"
              />
              <span class="guide-name">AIya</span>
            </div>
            <div class="guide-profile">
              <img
                src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-aion-icon.png"
                alt="AIon"
                width="100"
                height="100"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                class="guide-icon"
              />
              <span class="guide-name">AIon</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-guides-banner.png"
            alt="AIya and AIon - HeartStrings guides"
            width="480"
            height="320"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="guides-banner"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="guides-copy">
          <h2>AIya and AIon in the App</h2>
          <p>The same guides from the board game appear in the app as interactive companions. They are not just visual branding -- they represent the intelligence layer built on Deep Kore research.</p>
          <p>In the app, AIya and AIon will:</p>
          <ul class="guide-list">
            <li>Guide you through profile setup and preference calibration</li>
            <li>Explain match rationale in plain language</li>
            <li>Suggest conversation starters and connection prompts</li>
            <li>Maintain continuity between game sessions and digital interactions</li>
            <li>Provide transparency into why and how recommendations are made</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="honesty-note">Note: AIya and AIon in the app are currently in development. The UI exists. The live interaction layer is being built. No live AI responses are active yet.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- App Screen Preview -->
  <section class="screen-preview">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>App Design Preview</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">The login and onboarding UI is designed. The matching engine is under active development.</p>
      <div class="screens-row">
        <div class="screen-card">
          <img
            src="/heartstrings/heartstrings-app-signup.png"
            alt="HeartStrings App sign in screen"
            width="300"
            height="500"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="screen-img"
          />
          <div class="screen-label">Sign In</div>
        </div>
        <div class="screen-card screen-coming">
          <div class="coming-placeholder">
            <div class="coming-icon">profile</div>
            <div class="coming-text">Profile Setup</div>
            <div class="coming-badge">In Development</div>
          </div>
          <div class="screen-label">Profile</div>
        </div>
        <div class="screen-card screen-coming">
          <div class="coming-placeholder">
            <div class="coming-icon">match</div>
            <div class="coming-text">Match View</div>
            <div class="coming-badge">In Development</div>
          </div>
          <div class="screen-label">Matching</div>
        </div>
        <div class="screen-card screen-coming">
          <div class="coming-placeholder">
            <div class="coming-icon">chat</div>
            <div class="coming-text">Guided Chat</div>
            <div class="coming-badge">Planned</div>
          </div>
          <div class="screen-label">Connection</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Honest Status -->
  <section class="status-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Is Live and What Is Not</h2>
      <div class="status-grid">
        <div class="status-col live">
          <div class="col-label live">Done</div>
          <ul>
            <li>App logo and brand identity</li>
            <li>Sign in and onboarding UI (DS-1 design system)</li>
            <li>Custom HeartStringsAI font (UPM 1000)</li>
            <li>Profile system architecture</li>
            <li>80-question personality assessment</li>
            <li>6-bit binary vector privacy-preserving matching</li>
            <li>Date check-in module</li>
            <li>Availability module</li>
            <li>Reminder scheduler</li>
            <li>Determinism invariants 1-34 enforced</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="status-col indev">
          <div class="col-label indev">In Development</div>
          <ul>
            <li>AIya and AIon interaction layer</li>
            <li>ByteLite encoder integration points</li>
            <li>AI onboarding flow</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="status-col planned">
          <div class="col-label planned">Planned</div>
          <ul>
            <li>Closed beta with HeartStrings Play purchasers</li>
            <li>App Store and Play Store launch</li>
            <li>iOS-first release (future phase)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="app-cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <h2>Follow the App</h2>
        <p>The HeartStrings App will first be available to HeartStrings Play purchasers. Express interest or subscribe for development updates.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-rose">Express Interest</a>
          <a href="/subscribe" class="btn btn-outline">Subscribe for Updates</a>
          <a href="/heartstrings" class="btn btn-pink-outline">Explore HeartStrings Play</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* App Hero */
  .app-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 4rem 0 3.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-gradient {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 40%, rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 60%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.07) 0%, transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0A0E27 0%, #060813 100%);
  }

  .app-hero .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .dev-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.15);
    color: #A855F7;
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.4);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    display: block;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .hero-copy h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FB7185 0%, #EC4899 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(0.9375rem, 1.5vw, 1.125rem);
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.85);
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.6);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-preview {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .app-screen-img {
    width: 200px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.2), 0 0 0 1px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.15);
  }

  .screen-badge {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.35);
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .btn-rose {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FB7185 0%, #EC4899 100%);
    color: white;
  }
  .btn-rose:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.4); }

  .btn-pink-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #EC4899;
    border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.35);
  }
  .btn-pink-outline:hover {
    border-color: #EC4899;
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.25);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.5);
    color: #E0E0E0;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* What the App Does */
  .app-what {
    padding: 3.5rem 0;
    background: #060813;
  }

  .app-logo-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .app-logo-img {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .app-logo-row h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #FB7185;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .section-lead {
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.7);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-sub {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.7);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.2);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .feature-icon.pink { background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.12); color: #EC4899; border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.3); }
  .feature-icon.rose { background: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.12); color: #FB7185; border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.3); }
  .feature-icon.purple { background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.12); color: #A855F7; border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3); }
  .feature-icon.cyan { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); color: #00D4FF; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.25); }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.65);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Play Bridge */
  .play-bridge {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #060813 0%, rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.04) 50%, #060813 100%);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.1);
  }

  .bridge-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .bridge-flow {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .flow-step {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.7);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step-play { border: 1px solid rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.25); }
  .step-app { border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.3); }
  .step-infra { border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); }

  .flow-icon {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.25);
  }

  .flow-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #E0E0E0;
  }

  .step-play .flow-label { color: #EC4899; }
  .step-app .flow-label { color: #FB7185; }
  .step-infra .flow-label { color: #00D4FF; }

  .flow-step p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .flow-arrow {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.4);
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .bridge-caption {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.4);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Guides Section */
  .app-guides {
    padding: 3.5rem 0;
    background: #060813;
  }

  .guides-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .guide-pair {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .guide-profile {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .guide-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.15);
  }

  .guide-name {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.7);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .guides-banner {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.12);
  }

  .guides-copy h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .guides-copy p {
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.75);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .guide-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .guide-list li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.7);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .guide-list li::before {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #FB7185;
  }

  .honesty-note {
    font-size: 0.8125rem !important;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.4) !important;
    font-style: italic;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.3);
    padding-left: 0.875rem !important;
    margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
  }

  /* Screen Preview */
  .screen-preview {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #060813 0%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.02) 100%);
  }

  .screen-preview h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .screens-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .screen-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .screen-img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 200px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.15);
  }

  .screen-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.4);
  }

  .screen-coming {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .coming-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 200px;
    aspect-ratio: 2/3.3;
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .coming-icon {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.4);
  }

  .coming-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.4);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .coming-badge {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 0.18rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1);
    color: #A855F7;
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.25);
  }

  /* Status Section */
  .status-section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: #060813;
  }

  .status-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #E0E0E0;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .status-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

